WEBVTT

00:04:03.769 --> 00:04:07.006
Investigation and autopsy reports
eventually revealed

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:08.549
the sequence of events.

00:04:10.069 --> 00:04:12.776
Deah had just gotten
off the bus from class,

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:14.379
Razan was visiting for dinner,

00:04:14.403 --> 00:04:15.978
already at home with Yusor.

00:04:16.550 --> 00:04:19.384
As they began to eat,
they heard a knock on the door.

00:04:19.408 --> 00:04:21.436
When Deah opened it,

00:04:21.460 --> 00:04:24.211
their neighbor proceeded
to fire multiple shots at him.

00:04:26.787 --> 00:04:28.317
According to 911 calls,

00:04:28.341 --> 00:04:30.378
the girls were heard screaming.